data.description:
Step into this enchanting oasis! This turn-key gem boasts a split-floor plan & awe-inspiring mountain vistas from both front and back yards. Revel in the freshness of new flooring, and soak in the ambiance of freshly painted interiors, complemented by upgraded lighting.
The open layout graciously invites gatherings, ensuring space for everyone to revel in the festivities. Unwind in the spacious primary suite, complete with an adorable ensuite bath and an expansive walk-in closet.
Out back, a sprawling oasis awaits - a vast backyard adorned with brand-new pavers and vibrant, low-maintenance turf. A stone's throw from El Prado Park, relish in the convenience of a public pool and playground. Plus, enjoy the ease of strolling to the nearby elementary school.
This home offers not just comfort, but a lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this your own!
